{"tid":129753,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話而家d學生郁d就跳樓既人根本係on9","createTime":"2017-02-21T23:49:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-15T06:39:59.000Z","uid":84128,"like":85,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa3fc726be3718158782266ca371f45a05fbcf60","tid":129753,"uid":84128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T23:49:58.000Z","msg":"大佬 同你地個年代差左咁遠<br />\n好心貼返地少少得唔得<br />\n而家社會唔同左 風氣都唔同左<br />\n以前讀唔到書 都有其他路行<br />\n而家個個家長同人都鼓吹讀唔到大學就會乞食<br />\n比著你係個學生 自己又無能力讀<br />\n但大家都話讀唔到書係乞食 又無其他方向<br />\n係人都覺得唔知點算啦<br />\n讀唔到書唔係最大既壓力來源<br />\n係前境對佢地黎講先係最大既壓力來源<br />\n成日話努力讀書就入到大學<br />\n入唔到正廢柴<br />\n離哂地 根本現實就有一班人入唔到<br />\n係大學生都可以乞食既情況下<br />\n你想班深知自己無能力讀既學生可以點?<br />\n好心你地比上一輩吊完就唔好搞9埋下一輩啦<br />\n利申:讀緊大學 都唔知前境點樣好"},{"pid":"bd202191259cb7e9f992fc7b1f670bcfe0a5f61f","tid":129753,"uid":42374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-21T23:58:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac782111612abb7a80668dfce27d934726db5173","tid":129753,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T00:02:01.000Z","msg":"如果將來考不進三大/神科, 會不會跳樓"},{"pid":"e847e0c930db38b4111f7ba67d2d249ecc408ef5","tid":129753,"uid":70779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T00:03:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cd993ff56a4268e5554bfa9036ed039425dcca4","tid":129753,"uid":83941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T00:03:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0669284375cc6943fa4f543a01b9ca2b9c967392","tid":129753,"uid":62350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-22T00:05:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果將來考不進三大/神科, 會不會跳樓</blockquote><br />\n會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n到時香港會得番三大/神料